<h1><b>Leaving carrots and milk for Santa and his 7 reindeer</b></h1>

    <p>The final tradition of the day is leaving carrots and milk for Santa and his 7 reindeer. People do this for Santa as a gesture of gratitude for his hardwork,a way to teach children about giving,and a tradition rooted in historical gift-giving customs.</p>
